thread.title: Rachel Sulit
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Rachel Sulit

author: Rachel Sulit
title: Rachel Sulit
text:
this is our first time renting a storage unit. we shopped around and we feel that Public Storage is the least expensive. the location is nice too it's right between our old place and the new place that we are moving into! the property manager was very friendly but professional. she offered us the essentials that we need from moving to what kind of storage unit we need.
we are very satisfied customers!
